%5B%7B%22title%22%3A%22An%20air%20traffic%20controller%20was%20found%20asleep%20under%20a%20blanket%20mid-shift%20at%20one%20of%20the%20world's%20top%20airports%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22air%20traffic%20controller%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5178056469bedd9c6900000b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EShortage%20of%20air%20traffic%20controllers%20%3Cp%3EJoe%20Raedle%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EAn%20air%20traffic%20controller%20in%20Australia%20was%20found%20asleep%20under%20a%20blanket%20at%20the%20end%20of%20a%20shift.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHe%20had%20worked%20seven%20night%20shifts%20in%20nine%20days%20due%20to%20staffing%20changes%2C%20a%20safety%20investigation%20found.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20report%20said%20an%20%26quot%3Bunderlying%20lack%20of%20resources%26quot%3B%20contributed%20to%20the%20incident.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EAn%20air%20traffic%20controller%20at%20a%20major%20Australian%20airport%20was%20found%20asleep%20at%20the%20end%20of%20their%20night%20shift%20while%20they%20were%20the%20only%20person%20on%20duty%2C%20according%20to%20an%20investigation%20by%20the%20Australian%20Transport%20Safety%20Bureau%20(ATSB).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20worker%20had%20signed%20on%20for%20their%20night%20shift%2C%20which%20ran%20from%2010%20p.m.%20to%206%20a.m.%2C%20at%20the%20Brisbane%20Centre%2C%20a%20major%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbecoming-air-traffic-controller-career-pros-cons-of-job-2022-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eair%20traffic%20control%20center%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20Brisbane%20Airport.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBrisbane%20is%20Australia's%20third-busiest%20airport%3Cspan%3E%2C%20handling%20around%2022.6%20million%20passengers%20annually.%20It%20has%20consistently%20been%20among%20the%20100%20busiest%20airports%20in%20the%20world%20and%20was%20ranked%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.worldairportawards.com%2Fworlds-top-100-airports-2024%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eas%20the%20world's%2032nd-best%20by%20Skytrax%20in%202024%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20December%209%2C%202022%2C%20the%20morning%20shift%20controller%20arrived%20at%20work%20at%205%3A15%20a.m.%20to%20find%20their%20night%20shift%20counterpart%20asleep%20at%20the%20console.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20worker%20was%20discovered%20lying%20across%20two%20chairs%20with%20a%20blanket%20covering%20them%2C%20according%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.atsb.gov.au%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2F2024-09%2FAO-2022-065%2520%2528Final%2529.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20report%3C%2Fa%3E.%20They%20were%20still%20wearing%20their%20headset%2C%20and%20the%20air%20situation%20display%20(ASD)%20screensaver%20was%20on.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20ensuring%20there%20was%20no%20traffic%20in%20the%20area%2C%20the%20station%20was%20handed%20over%20to%20the%20oncoming%20controller.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20noted%20that%20the%20Brisbane%20Centre%20building%20was%20cooler%20at%20night%2C%20and%20it%20was%20considered%20normal%20practice%20for%20blankets%20to%20be%20used%20during%20night%20shifts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20ATSB's%20report%20blamed%20multiple%20night%20shifts%20in%20a%20short%20space%20of%20time%2C%20the%20worker's%20low%20workload%2C%20and%20an%20ineffective%20risk%20management%20system%20for%20the%20incident.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20noted%20that%20the%20worker%20had%2010%20years%20of%20experience%20as%20a%20controller%20and%20had%20been%20in%20their%20current%20position%20for%20three%20years.%20However%2C%20due%20to%20last%20minute%20roster%20changes%2C%20they%20had%20worked%20their%20seventh%20night%20shift%20in%20nine%20days%20and%20had%20not%20taken%20the%20recommended%20rest%20period%20in%20between.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fplatform.twitter.com%2Fwidgets.js%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22twitter%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EA%20Brisbane%20Centre%20air%20traffic%20controller%20who%20was%20found%20asleep%20at%20their%20workstation%20towards%20the%20end%20of%20their%20shift%20had%20worked%20multiple%20consecutive%20night%20shifts%20resulting%20in%20sleep%20debt%2C%20an%20ATSB%20investigation%20report%20details.%3C%2Fp%3E%E2%80%94%20ATSB%20(%40atsbgovau)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fatsbgovau%2Fstatus%2F1830791268907278639%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3ESeptember%203%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20had%20been%20no%20traffic%20or%20scheduled%20flights%20in%20the%20airspace%20the%20controller%20was%20responsible%20for%20and%20a%20system%20supervisor%20had%20been%20on%20duty%20at%20the%20front%20desk%20of%20the%20center.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20report%20found%20that%20cumulative%20fatigue%20was%20not%20being%20effectively%20managed%20at%20the%20center.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLikely%20due%20to%20an%20underlying%20lack%20of%20resources%20within%20Airservices%20Australia%2C%20there%20was%20an%20over-reliance%20on%20tactical%20changes%20to%20manage%20the%20roster%2C%26quot%3B%20investigators%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20ATSB%20said%20it%20would%20update%20its%20safety%20procedures%20and%20fatigue%20risk%20management%20regulations%20in%20response%20to%20the%20incident.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAirservices%20Australia%2C%20which%20runs%20the%20Brisbane%20Centre%2C%20has%20increased%20the%20overall%20number%20of%20air%20traffic%20controllers%20and%20enhanced%20internal%20processes%20since%20the%20incident%2C%20according%20to%20the%20report.%20The%20ATSB%20will%20continue%20to%20monitor%20the%20issue.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20US%2C%20fatigue%20has%20been%20a%20growing%20safety%20concern%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fairport-collision-close-call-solutions-sleep-runways-air-traffic-controllers-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eshortages%20of%20air%20traffic%20controllers%3C%2Fa%3E%20have%20driven%20up%20the%20amount%20of%20overtime%20required%20for%20those%20that%20remain.%20Some%20controllers%20have%20turned%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fair-traffic-controllers-workload-stress-alcohol-drugs-faa-close-calls-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Ealcohol%20and%20sleeping%20pills%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20cope%20with%20their%20grueling%20schedules.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELast%20year%2C%20The%20New%20York%20Times%20found%20that%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fairline-close-calls-happening-multiple-times-nyt-investigation-2023-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Enear-misses%20between%20aircraft%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20were%20happening%20more%20often%20than%20previously%20thought.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAirservices%20Australia%20did%20not%20immediately%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment%20from%20Business%20Insider%2C%20sent%20outside%20regular%20Australian%20working%20hours.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Faustralian-air-traffic-controller-asleep-mid-shift-brisbane-2024-9%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1725359215000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66d6c6d1289b805d1db3786a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Faustralian-air-traffic-controller-asleep-mid-shift-brisbane-2024-9%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20safety%20report%20found%20that%20the%20worker%20had%20worked%20seven%20night%20shifts%20in%20nine%20days.%20He%20was%20covered%20in%20a%20blanket%2C%20it%20said.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22pthompson%40insider.com%20(Polly%20Thompson)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Faustralian-air-traffic-controller-asleep-mid-shift-brisbane-2024-9%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22We%20asked%204%20DINKs%20how%20they%20make%20new%20child-free%20friends%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221192%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Two%20couples%20with%20dogs%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66d211d51d8d2deb96b7d8e2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22894%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EOn%20left%2C%20Bing%20Gonzalez%20with%20her%20husband%20and%20their%20dog.%20On%20right%2C%20Sandra%20Kushnir%20with%20her%20husband%20and%20their%20dog.%3Cp%3EBing%20Gonzales%2FSandra%20Kushnir%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EChildfree%20couples%2C%20or%20DINKs%2C%20can%20sometimes%20feel%20lonely%20when%20their%20friends%20start%20having%20kids.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EBut%20some%20DINKs%20find%20their%2030s%20to%20be%20a%20great%20time%20for%20making%20new%20friends.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EDINKs%20find%20friends%20by%20pursuing%20new%20hobbies%20and%20being%20open%20to%20age-gap%20friendships.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20early%20stages%20of%20their%20relationship%2C%20Bing%20Gonzalez%20and%20her%20husband%20always%20assumed%20they'd%20have%20kids.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20once%20they%20were%20married%20and%20settled%20enough%20to%20try%2C%20they%20decided%20against%20it%2C%20at%20least%20for%20the%20near%20future.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELike%20many%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Falices-dinks-henrys-fires-economy-guide-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emillennial%20DINKs%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20dual-income%20couples%20with%20no%20kids%20%E2%80%94%20the%20couple%20uses%20their%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fparents-dinks-winning-childfree-economy-finances-income-vacation-retirement-kids-