0referred%20to%20the%20rape%20of%20a%2020-year-old%20Dalit%20woman%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh's%20Hathras%20in%202020%20and%20the%20rape%20and%20barbaric%20slaughter%20of%20a%20college%20student%20in%20Bengal's%20North%2024%20Parganas%20district%20in%202013%2C%20as%20well%20as%20the%20rape%20of%20a%20child%20last%20week%20at%20a%20government-run%20hospital%20in%20Rajasthan's%20Jaipur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20the%20Kamduni%20case%20(the%20North%2024%20Parganas%20rape)%20we%20demanded%20capital%20punishment...%20but%20the%20matter%20is%20pending%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20(where%20an%20appeal%20has%20been%20filed%20after%20the%20Calcutta%20High%20Court%20acquitted%20one%20accused%20and%20commuted%20the%20death%20sentence%20of%20two%20others).%20No%20one%20talks%20about%20what%20happened%20in%20Unnao%20(and)%20the%20victim%20of%20Hathras%20did%20not%20get%20justice...%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20%26quot%3Babnormally%20high%20crime%20rates%20against%20women%20in%20states%20like%20UP%20and%20Gujarat...%20and%20there%20is%20no%20justice%20there%20but%20in%20Bengal%20women%20will%20get%20justice%20in%20courts%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20thundered%20in%20the%20Assembly%2C%20as%20she%20also%20demanded%20the%20resignation%20of%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20and%20Home%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah%2C%20as%20well%20as%20chief%20ministers%20of%20all%20states%20%26quot%3Bunable%20to%20implement%20effective%20legislations%20to%20safeguard%20women%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20mention%20of%20Mr%20Modi%20and%20Mr%20Shah%20triggered%20loud%20protests%20from%20BJP%20lawmakers%2C%20to%20which%20Ms%20Banerjee%20asked%2C%20%26quot%3BWhat%20if%20I%20raise%20slogans%20against%20PM%20and%20Home%20Minister%20as%20you%20raise%20against%20me...%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Banerjee's%20sharp%20comments%20came%20as%20her%20Trinamool%20tabled%20a%20new%20law%2C%20which%20will%20make%20rape%20a%20crime%20commensurate%20with%20murder%20for%20which%20punishment%20will%20be%20death%20or%20life%20in%20jail.%20She%20said%20the%20%26quot%3Bhistoric%26quot%3B%20new%20law%20-%20called%20the%20Aparajita%20law%20-%20will%20ensure%20fast-tracked%20investigations%20and%20stricter%20punishments.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20name%20of%20the%20new%20law%20has%20been%20seen%20by%20many%20as%20an%20homage%20to%20the%20young%20woman%20who%20was%20raped%20and%20murdered%20in%20North%2024%20Parganas%3B%20according%20to%20reports%20her%20name%20was%20Aparajita.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Aparajita%20law%20will%20%26quot%3Bplug%20loopholes%26quot%3B%20in%20laws%20passed%20by%20the%20centre%2C%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20said%2C%20taking%20a%20swipe%20at%20its%20much-vaunted%20set%20of%20three%20new%20criminal%20laws.%20Rape%20is%20a%20curse%20against%20humanity%20(and)%20social%20reforms%20are%20required%20to%20stop%20such%20crimes...%26quot%3B%20she%20said%2C%20urging%20Governor%20CV%20Ananda%20Bose%2C%20who%20has%20also%20taken%20pot%20shots%20at%20the%20Trinamool%20on%20the%20RG%20Kar%20Hospital%20case%2C%20to%20sign%20the%20bill%20without%20delay.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%2C%20in%20a%20pointed%20remark%20at%20the%20BJP%20-%20which%20has%20been%20relentless%20in%20targeting%20her%20but%20has%20offered%20support%2C%20of%20a%20sort%2C%20on%20this%20legislation%20-%20she%20called%20on%20the%20opposition%20to%20also%20urge%20the%20Governor.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20want%20justice%20from%20the%20CBI...%20CBI%20should%20hang%20the%20criminal%2C%26quot%3B%20Ms%20Banerjee%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bill%20was%20passed%20shortly%20after%20the%20Chief%20Minister's%20speech%2C%20but%20not%20before%20the%20BJP's%20Suvendu%20Adhikari%2C%20her%20former%20aide%20and%20now%20the%20Leader%20of%20the%20Opposition%2C%20criticised%20it%20as%20being%20tabled%20in%20haste.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20the%20BJP%20would%20support%20the%20bill%2C%20but%20also%20demand%20accountability%20from%20Ms%20Banerjee.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20will%20support...%20but%20why%20did%20you%20bring%20this%20in%20haste%3F%20We%20could%20have%20sent%20it%20to%20a%20committee%20(for%20further%20study).%20We%20want%20punishment%20for%20the%20culprits.%20We%20will%20not%20seek%20division...%20but%20the%20state%20government%20will%20have%20to%20ensure%20the%20bill%20is%20made%20effective%20at%20the%20earliest%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Adhikari%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CBI%20is%20investigating%20this%20case%20pursuant%20to%20a%20direction%20from%20the%20Calcutta%20High%20Court%2C%20which%20ruffled%20political%20feathers%20by%20overruling%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20and%20summoning%20the%20central%20agency.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20was%20a%20day%20after%20Ms%20Banerjee%20gave%20Kolkata%20Police%20a%20week's%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20then%20Ms%20Banerjee%20has%20been%20demanding%20results%20from%20the%20CBI%2C%20which%20made%20its%20first%20arrest%20late%20last%20night%3B%20Dr%20Sandip%20Ghosh%2C%20the%20former%20Principal%20of%20the%20RG%20Kar%20Hospital%2C%20was%20arrested%20after%20two%20weeks%20of%20questioning.%20Dr%20Ghosh%2C%20though%2C%20was%20arrested%20over%20allegations%20of%20financial%20irregularities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CBI%20also%20arrested%20three%20others%2C%20including%20a%20security%20guard.%20But%20the%20only%20arrest%2C%20so%20far%2C%20connected%20to%20the%20rape%20and%20murder%20has%20been%20by%20Kolkata%20Police%2C%20who%20arrested%20a%20civilian%20volunteer%2C%20Sanjoy%20Roy.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1725354600000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2Fqived17_mamata-banerjee_625x300_28_August_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmamata-banerjee-cites-unnao-hathras-in-statement-on-kolkata-rape-6479938%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Bengal%20Chief%20Minister%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20-%20under%20fire%20over%20the%20rape%20and%20murder%20of%20a%20doctor%20at%20Kolkata's%20RG%20Kar%20Hospital%20