nk.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSometimes%20there%20will%20be%20multiple%20ships%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt%20could%20be%20a%20long%20walk%20from%20where%20your%20ship%20is%20docked%20all%20the%20way%20back%20to%20the%20main%20street%20area.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBefore%20you%20disembark%20at%20the%20end%20of%20a%20cruise%2C%20don't%20forget%20to%20tip%20the%20crew.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Deck%2016%20on%20the%20world's%20largest%20cruise%20ship%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F625ef5abd2039d0019ba61ea%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222250%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ECruisers%20at%20a%20bar%20on%20a%20ship.%3Cp%3EJoey%20Hadden%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20vast%20majority%20of%20cruise%20lines%20now%20have%20the%20option%20for%20you%20to%20prepay%20tips%2C%20or%20they%20have%20what%20they%20call%20an%20'additional%20daily%20service'%20charge%20that's%20added%20to%20your%20account%20per%20person%20per%20day%2C%26quot%3B%20Bucolo%20said.%20%26quot%3BPlenty%20of%20people%20who%20cruise%20a%20lot%20take%20it%20off.%20We%20don't%20recommend%20that.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBucolo%20added%20that%20he%20often%20gives%20an%20extra%20tip%20to%20crew%20members%20he%20interacts%20with%20throughout%20the%20journey.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe'll%20tip%20the%20people%20in%20the%20restaurants.%20If%20we%20frequent%20a%20bar%2C%20we%20usually%20tip%20those%20bartenders%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BBut%20that%20stateroom%20attendant%20is%20who%20we%20interact%20with%20the%20most.%20They%20make%20up%20the%20room%20at%20least%20once%20a%20day.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20recommended%20tipping%20your%20stateroom%20attendant%20%245%20to%20%2410%20per%20person%20per%20night.%20He%20tips%20servers%20and%20bar%20tenders%2018%25%20to%2020%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThroughout%20your%20cruise%2C%20chill%20o