2%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fi-ask-for-forgiveness-benjamin-netanyahu-on-death-of-israeli-hostages-6480159%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Inside%20The%20World's%20Largest%20Palace%20Which%20Will%20Host%20PM%20Modi%20On%20Brunei%20Visit%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EPrime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20is%20on%20a%20two-day%20visit%20to%20Brunei%2C%20the%20first%20by%20an%20Indian%20PM.%20On%20his%20visit%20to%20the%20Southeast%20Asian%20nation%2C%20PM%20Modi%20will%20meet%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fpm-narendra-modi-to-meet-with-the-sultan-of-brunei-who-boasts-world-s-largest-car-collection-worth-5b-6478680%23pfrom%3Dhome-ndtv_topstories%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESultan%20Hassanal%20Bolkiah%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20ruler%20of%20Brunei%2C%20at%20his%20official%20residence%2C%20the%20Istana%20Nurul%20Iman%20Palace.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnThe%20Istana%20Nurul%20Iman%20Palace%2C%20located%20near%20Brunei's%20capital%2C%20Bandar%20Seri%20Begawan%2C%20is%20the%20world's%20largest%20residential%20palace%20and%20has%20its%20name%20registered%20in%20Guinness%20World%20Records.%20It%20boasts%201%2C788%20rooms%2C%20257%20bathrooms%20and%2044%20staircases%20made%20of%2038%20kinds%20of%20marble.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cstrong%3EHistory%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnIstana%20Nurul%20Iman%2C%20translating%20to%20%26quot%3BPalace%20of%20the%20Light%20of%20Faith%2C%26quot%3B%20was%20commissioned%20by%20Sultan%20Hassanal%20Bolkiah%20in%201981.%20The%20construction%2C%20costing%20approximately%20%241.4%20billion%2C%20was%20completed%20by%201984%2C%20just%20before%20Brunei's%20independence%20from%20British%20rule.%20Designed%20by%20Filipino%20architect%20Leonardo%20Locsin%2C%20the%20palace%20was%20intended%20to%20reflect%20a%20new%20era%20of%20the%20country.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cstrong%3EFeatures%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnThe%20structure%20spans%20a%20mammoth%202%2C00%2C000%20square%20meters%2C%20making%20it%20the%20largest%20residential%20palace%20in%20the%20world.%20It%20has%201%2C788%20rooms%2C%20including%20257%20bathrooms%2C%20and%20features%20a%20banquet%20hall%20capable%20of%20hosting%205%2C000%20guests.%20The%20palace%20also%20has%20parking%20space%20for%20110%20cars%2C%20an%20air-conditioned%20stable%20for%20200%20polo%20ponies%2C%20five%20swimming%20pools%2C%20and%20a%20mosque%20that%20can%20accommodate%201%2C500%20worshippers.%20The%2044%20staircases%20within%20the%20palace%20are%20constructed%20from%2038%20different%20types%20of%20marble.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cstrong%3EArchitectural%20Style%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnThe%20palace's%20architectural%20design%20is%20a%20blend%20of%20Brunei's%20Islamic%20culture%20and%20Malay%20traditions.%20The%20grand%20white%20exterior%20is%20complemented%20by%20golden%20domes%2C%20including%20a%20central%20dome%20studded%20with%2022-carat%20gold.%20The%20interior%2C%20designed%20by%20Khuan%20Chew%2C%20who%20also%20contributed%20to%20designing%20Dubai's%20Burj%20Al%20Arab%2C%20is%20adorned%20with%20gold%20and%20marble.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnIt%20has%20hosted%20several%20events%2C%20including%20the%2028th%20Asia-Pacific%20Economic%20Cooperation%20(APEC)%20Economic%20Leaders'%20Meeting%2C%20held%20virtually%20from%20this%20grand%20setting.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnWhile%20Istana%20Nurul%20Iman%20is%20the%20world's%20largest%20residential%20palace%2C%20it%20is%20not%20the%20most%20expensive.%20That%20distinction%20belongs%20to%20Buckingham%20Palace%20in%20London%2C%20valued%20at%20approximately%20%242.9%20billion.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1725352860000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-09%2Fl1nnp4uo_istana-nurul-iman_625x300_03_September_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fpm-narendra-modi-to-meet-brunei-sultan-at-istana-nurul-iman-the-world