os-of-her-ex-after-breakup-says-kourtney-kardashian-did-something-similar%2Farticleshow%2F113016523.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BContent%20According%20To%20Nation's%20Sentiments%26quot%3B%3A%20Centre-Netflix%20Meet%20On%20IC%20814%20Series%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ENetflix%20India%20has%20assured%20Centre%20that%20in%20the%20future%2C%20content%20will%20be%20in%20accordance%20with%20%26quot%3Bnation's%20sentiments%26quot%3B%2C%20sources%20have%20said.%20The%20OTT%20giant's%20assurance%20comes%20at%20the%20back%20of%20a%20row%20involving%20its%20web%20series%20'IC%20814%20Kandahar%20Hijack'.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20series%2C%20which%20revisits%20the%201999%20hijacking%20of%20an%20Indian%20Airlines%20flight%20by%20Pakistan-based%20terror%20outfit%20Harkat-ul-Mujahideen%2C%20has%20triggered%20a%20fierce%20backlash%2C%20culminating%20in%20an%20hour-long%20meeting%20between%20the%20streaming%20giant%20and%20the%20Centre.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDirected%20by%20Anubhav%20Sinha%20and%20released%20on%20August%2029%2C%20it%20portrays%20the%20hijackers%20of%20the%20ill-fated%20flight%20in%20a%20manner%20that%20has%20drawn%20ire%20from%20various%20quarters%2C%20particularly%20due%20to%20the%20alleged%20alteration%20of%20their%20names%20to%20%26quot%3BBhola%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3BShankar%2C%26quot%3B%20traditionally%20associated%20with%20Lord%20Shiva.%20This%20depiction%20has%20been%20perceived%20as%20a%20distortion%20of%20historical%20facts%2C%20with%20critics%20arguing%20that%20it%20misrepresents%20the%20real%20identities%20of%20the%20terrorists%2C%20thereby%20offending%20Hindu%20sentiments.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EExplained%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20%7C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fexplained-controversy-surrounding-netflixs-ic-814-the-kandahar-hijack-6471958%5C%22%3EControversy%20Surrounding%20Netflix's%20'IC%20814%3A%20The%20Kandahar%20Hijack'%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20release%20of%20'IC%20814%3A%20The%20Kandahar%20Hijack'%20has%20also%20ignited%20a%20war%20of%20words%20on%20social%20media.%20BJP%20IT%20Cell%20chief%20Amit%20Malviya%20accused%20the%20filmmakers%20of%20furthering%20an%20agenda%20to%20whitewash%20the%20crimes%20of%20Pakistani%20terrorists%20by%20giving%20them%20Hindu%20names%2C%20thereby%20misleading%20future%20generations.%20On%20the%20other%20side%2C%20former%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20Chief%20Minister%20Omar%20Abdullah%20and%20Shiv%20Sena-UBT%20leader%20Priyanka%20Chaturvedi%20criticised%20the%20outrage%20as%20selective%2C%20pointing%20out%20the%20inconsistencies%20in%20demands%20for%20historical%20accuracy%20in%20cinema.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20platforms%20like%20X%20(formerly%20Twitter)%2C%20hashtags%20such%20as%20%23BoycottNetflix%20and%20%23BoycottBollywood%20began%20trending%2C%20with%20users%20accusing%20the%20filmmakers%20of%20rewriting%20history%20and%20downplaying%20the%20terror%20inflicted%20by%20the%20actual%20hijackers.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20a%20Union%20Home%20Ministry%20document%2C%20released%20in%20the%20immediate%20aftermath%20of%20the%201999%20hijacking%20has%20set%20the%20record%20straight.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20statement%20categorically%20states%20that%20the%20hijackers%20-%20Sunny%20Ahmed%20Qazi%2C%20Shakir%20a.k.a%20Rajesh%20Gopal%20Verma%2C%20Mistri%20Zahoor%20Ibrahim%2C%20Shahid%20Akhtar%20Sayed%20and%20Ibrahim%20Athar%20used%20nicknames%20like%20Bhola%2C%20Shankar%2C%20Doctor%20and%20Burger%20to%20address%20each%20other%20inside%20the%20plane.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTo%20the%20passengers%20of%20the%20hijacked%20place%20these%20hijackers%20came%20to%20be%20known%20respectively%20as%20(1)%20Chief%2C%20(2)%20Doctor%2C%20(3)%20Burger%2C%20(4)%20Bhola%20and%20(5)%20Shankar%2C%20the%20names%20by%20which%20the%20hijackers%20invariably%20addressed%20one%20another%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20government%20statement%20reads.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20parallel%20development%2C%20actor-turned-politician%20Kangana%20Ranaut's%20upcoming%20film%20'Emergency'%20has%20also%20come%20under%20scrutiny.%20Ms%20Ranaut%20stars%20as%20former%20prime%20minister%20Indira%20Gandhi%20in%20the%20film%20which%20is%20based%20on%20the%2021-month%20emergency%20that%20was%20imposed%20from%201975%20to%201977.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Shiromani%20Gurdwara%20Prabandhak%20Committee%20(SGPC)%2C%20a%20top%20Sikh%20religious%20body%2C%20has%20raised%20objections%20to%20the%20film%2C%20necessitating%20a%20delay%20in%20its%20release%20as%20the%20CBFC%20considers%20the%20concerns.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20a%20delay%20in%20certification%2C%20Ms%20Ranaut%20said%20it's%20%26quot%3Bhugely%20demotivating%20and%20unjust%26quot%3B%20that%20censorship%20is%20only%20for%20those%20like%20her%20who%20%26quot%3Bmake%20films%20on%20historical%20facts%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReferring%20to%20'IC%20814%3A%20The%20Kandahar%20Hijack'%2C%20Ms%20Ranaut%20said%20on%20X%20that%20%26quot%3Bone%20can%20show%20unimaginable%20amount%20of%20violence%20and%20nudity%20on%20OTT%20platforms%20without%20any%20consequence%20or%20censorship%2C%20one%20can%20even%20distort%20real-life%20events%20to%20suit%20their%20politically%20motivated%20sinister%20motives%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1725349860000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-09%2Fpursivuo_netflix-ic-814-kandahar-_625x300_02_September_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcontent-will-be-reviewed-sources-on-netflix-centre-meeting-on-ic-814-emergency-row-6479206%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Netflix%20India%20has%20assured%20Centre%20that%20in%20the%20future%2C%20content%20will%20be%20in%20accordance%20with%20%26quot%3Bnation's%20sentiments%26quot%3B%2C%20sources%20have%20said.%20The%20OTT%20giant's%20assurance%20comes%20at%20the%20back%20of%20a%20row%20involving%20its%20web%20series%20'IC%20814%20Kandahar%20Hijack'.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%