and%20playing%20politics%20during%20the%20calamity%2C%20Mr%20Reddy%20told%20the%20media%2C%20%26quot%3BKCR%20did%20not%20get%20out%20of%20his%20farmhouse%20and%20KTR%20is%20merrily%20tweeting%20during%20his%20holiday%20in%20the%20US.%26quot%3B%20The%20Chief%20Minister%20said%20he%20and%20his%20ministers%20are%20working%20on%20the%20ground%20to%20assist%20people.%20Mr%20Reddy%20has%20been%20visiting%20flood-hit%20areas%20and%20putting%20out%20messages%20to%20assure%20the%20people%20that%20the%20government%20stands%20by%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EState%20minister%20Ponguleti%20Srinivas%20Reddy%20said%20the%20state%20government%20has%20documentary%20evidence%20to%20show%20that%20choppers%20could%20not%20fly%20to%20the%20affected%20areas%20due%20to%20bad%20weather.%20He%2C%20however%2C%20admitted%20that%20the%20unavailability%20of%20choppers%20hit%20rescue%20operations%20and%20led%20to%20loss%20of%20lives.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20least%2016%20people%20have%20been%20killed%20in%20Telangana%20floods%20so%20far%20and%20property%20worth%20Rs%205%2C000%20damaged.%20Chief%20Minister%20Reddy%20has%20urged%20the%20Centre%20to%20declare%20floods%20in%20the%20state%20a%20natural%20calamity%20and%20provide%20immediate%20assistance%20of%20Rs%202%2C000%20crore.%20The%20state%20government%20has%20announced%20Rs%205%20lakh%20compensation%20for%20the%20families%20of%20those%20killed%20in%20the%20calamity%20and%20Rs%2010%2C000%20per%20acre%20assistance%20for%20crop%20damage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EState%20minister%20for%20Women%20and%20Child%20Development%20Seethaka%20has%20countered%20the%20BRS'%20criticism%20on%20the%20compensation%20amount.%20%26quot%3BWhy%20didn't%20they%20give%20Rs%2025%20lakh%20to%20the%20flood%20victims%20when%20they%20were%20in%20power%3F%20Leaders%20who%20have%20been%20in%20power%20for%2010%20years%20and%20did%20not%20give%20a%20penny%20in%20compensation%20are%20spreading%20poison%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20has%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1725