ne.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20World%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fdid-kamala-harris-fake-accent-in-her-teachers-union-speech-social-media-reacts%2Farticleshow%2F113009627.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia-indiatimes-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fdid-kamala-harris-fake-accent-in-her-teachers-union-speech-social-media-reacts%2Famp_articleshow%2F113009627.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fdid-kamala-harris-fake-accent-in-her-teachers-union-speech-social-media-reacts%2Famp_articleshow%2F113009627.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22How%20Son%20Of%20Iran's%20Ayatollah%20Khamenei's%20Advisor%20Became%20An%20Oil%20Tycoon%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EHossein%20Shamkhani%2C%20the%20son%20of%20Iran's%20former%20national%20security%20chief%2C%20has%20emerged%20as%20a%20major%20player%20in%20the%20global%20oil%20market%2C%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Fnews%2Ffeatures%2F2024-08-30%2Firan-oil-secretive-trader-called-hector-seen-as-global-kingpin%5C%22%3EBloomberg%20report%3C%2Fa%3E%20says.%20Despite%20stringent%20US%20sanctions%20targeting%20Iranian%20and%20Russian%20oil%2C%20Shamkhani%20has%20managed%20to%20run%20international%20oil%20trading%20operations%20from%20the%20heart%20of%20Dubai.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShamkhani's%20rise%20to%20prominence%20is%20inextricably%20linked%20to%20his%20father%2C%20Ali%20Shamkhani%2C%20a%20key%20figure%20in%20Iran's%20defence%20and%20security%20apparatus.%20Ali%20Shamkhani%2C%20who%20served%20as%20the%20Secretary%20of%20Iran's%20Supreme%20National%20Security%20Council%20(SNSC)%20for%20nearly%20a%20decade%2C%20continues%20to%20hold%20sway%20as%20an%20advisor%20to%20Supreme%20Leader%20Ayatollah%20Ali%20Khamenei.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20elder%20Shamkhani%20has%20maintained%20a%20formidable%20presence%20in%20Iran's%20political%20landscape%2C%20his%20son%20has%20quietly%20built%20a%20business%20empire%20that%20now%20commands%20significant%20influence%20in%20global%20energy%20markets.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Dubai%20Connection%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Bloomberg%2C%20two%20years%20ago%2C%20a%20relatively%20unknown%20company%2C%20Milavous%20Group%20Ltd%2C%20leased%20a%20premium%20office%20space%20in%20a%20Dubai%20corporate%20tower.%20Within%20months%2C%20the%20firm%20had%20carved%20out%20a%20substantial%20role%20in%20the%20global%20oil%20market.%20According%20to%20sources%20familiar%20with%20the%20company's%20operations%2C%20Hossein%20Shamkhani%2C%20who%20operates%20under%20the%20pseudonym%20%26quot%3BHector%26quot%3B%20in%20trading%20circles%2C%20is%20the%20driving%20force%20behind%20Milavous%2C%20the%20report%20stated.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrom%20its%20strategic%20base%20in%20Dubai%2C%20Milavous%20has%20reportedly%20generated%20billions%20in%20revenue%20by%20selling%20commodities%20sourced%20from%20Iran%2C%20Russia%2C%20and%20other%20nations.%20The%20firm%20reportedly%20operates%20by%20blending%20and%20rebranding%20crude%20oil%2C%20often%20obscuring%20the%20origin%20of%20the%20products%20and%20complicating%20efforts%20to%20enforce%20international%20sanctions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EInfluence%20and%20Evasion%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShamkhani's%20network%2C%20described%20by%20insiders%20as%20one%20of%20the%20largest%20oil%20trading%20entities%20in%20Iran%2C%20has%20managed%20to%20evade%20US%20sanctions%20through%20a%20combination%20of%20legal%20loopholes%2C%20strategic%20partnerships%2C%20and%20a%20global%20network%20of%20shell%20companies.%20While%20Shamkhani%20himself%20is%20not%20subject%20to%20US%20sanctions%2C%20several%20vessels%20believed%20to%20be%20under%20his%20control%20have%20been%20targeted%20by%20the%20US%20Treasury%20Department.%20However%2C%20the%20sheer%20scale%20of%20his%20operations%2C%20involving%20over%2060%20ships%2C%20has%20made%20it%20difficult%20for%20US%20authorities%20to%20completely%20dismantle%20his%20network.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMilavous%2C%20under%20Shamkhani's%20guidance%2C%20has%20also%20expanded%20its%20reach%20into%20major%20international%20markets%2C%20reportedly%20supplying%20oil%20to%20global%20energy%20giants%20like%20China's%20Sinopec%2C%20Chevron%2C%20and%20BP%2C%20the%20report%20says.%20These%20companies%2C%20however%2C%20maintain%20that%20they%20comply%20with%20all%20relevant%20laws%20and%20sanctions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20government's%20efforts%20to%20clamp%20down%20on%20Shamkhani's%20activities%20have%20been%20complicated%20by%20the%20potential%20economic%20repercussions.%20With%20Iran's%20oil%20exports%20estimated%20to%20generate%20%2435%20billion%20annually%2C%20any%20significant%20disruption%20could%20have%20ripple%20effects%20across%20global%20energy%20markets%2C%20particularly%20during%20an%20election%20year%20in%20the%20US%20when%20fuel%20prices%20are%20under%20scrutiny.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1725336300000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-09%2Fj0dc4m2g_ali-shamkhani-_625x300_03_September_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fhow-son-of-irans-ayatollah-khameneis-advisor-became-an-oil-tycoon-6478434%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Hossein%20Shamkhani%2C%20the%20son%20of%20Iran's%20former%20national%20security%20chief%2C%20has%20emerged%20as%20a%20major%20player%20in%20the%20global%20oil%20market%2C%20a%20Bloomberg%20report%20says.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fhow-son-of-irans-ayatollah-khameneis-advisor-became-an-oil-tycoon-6478434%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Manta%20Webtoon%20Platform%20to%20Add%20300%20Titles%20Over%20Coming%20Year%2C%20Upgrade%20Creator%20Payment%20System%20(EXCLUSIVE)%22%2C%22content