20say%20which%20vehicles%20would%20have%20passed%20at%20the%20point%20of%20accident%20at%20this%20speed.%20This%20would%20essentially%20narrow%20down%20the%20suspect%20list%20to%20four%20or%20five%20vehicles%2C%20making%20investigation%20easier%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20major%20area%20where%20AI%20will%20play%20a%20huge%20role%20is%20in%20organised%20crime%20cases%20like%20narcotics%2C%20human%20trafficking%2C%20wildlife%20trade.%20These%20cases%20come%20with%20massive%20amounts%20of%20data%20across%20several%20years%2C%20including%20financial%20transactions%2C%20communication%20records%2C%20and%20surveillance%20footage.%20AI%E2%80%99s%20ability%20to%20perform%20relationship%20mapping%20and%20pattern%20recognition%20makes%20it%20an%20invaluable%20tool%20in%20these%20complex%20investigations%2C%20explains%20Harssh.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20AI%20can%20process%20and%20analyse%20data%20at%20scales%20beyond%20human%20capability%2C%20the%20technology%20is%20still%20in%20its%20early%20stages.%20The%20more%20data%20AI%20algorithms%20are%20exposed%20to%2C%20the%20more%20refined%20and%20accurate%20they%20become%2C%20just%20like%20Raven%20Sentry%20proved.%20Initially%2C%20while%20the%20predictions%20weren%E2%80%99t%20correct%2C%20as%20and%20when%20the%20data%20increased%2C%20it%20predicted%20an%20attack%20in%20Jalalabad%2C%20Afghanistan%2C%20which%20occurred%20a%20few%20days%20later.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMARVEL%E2%80%99s%20long-term%20goal%20is%20to%20perfect%20these%20algorithms%20over%20time%2C%20ensuring%20that%20they%20can%20eventually%20provide%20near-flawless%20support%20to%20law%20enforcement%20agencies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20technology%20continues%20to%20evolve%2C%20MARVEL%E2%80%99s%20work%20today%20is%20setting%20the%20stage%20for%20a%20future%20where%20AI%20and%20human%20expertise%20work%20hand%20in%20hand%20to%20maintain%20law%20and%20order.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%