20your%20relationship%20with%20work%20is%20great%20too%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Harpreet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHow%20do%20we%20raise%20fearless%20children%20if%20we%20are%20fearful%20ourselves%2C%20he%20argues%3F%20This%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20mean%20that%20you%20leave%20your%20child%20to%20do%20whatever%20they%20want.%20The%20idea%20is%20not%20to%20raise%20a%20consumer%2C%20but%20a%20person%20who%20has%20intrinsic%20motivation%20to%20do%20things.%20The%20best%20way%20to%20do%20that%20is%20by%20setting%20an%20example.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%E2%80%99s%20important%20for%20parents%20to%20walk%20the%20talk%2C%E2%80%9D%20agrees%20the%20school%20director.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20don%E2%80%99t%20want%20to%20have%20any%20regrets.%20I%20intend%20to%20live%20my%20one%20life%20to%20the%20best%20of%20my%20ability%2C%20and%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20want%20to%20wish%20that%20I%20was%20doing%20something%20else.%20I%20feel%20joyful%2C%20which%20is%20what%20my%20daughter%20also%20sees.%20My%20mind%20and%20body%20are%20aligned%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds%2C%20in%20hopes%20that%20building%20a%20better%20%E2%80%98you%E2%80%99%20will%20help%20you%20build%20a%20better%20relationship%20with%20your%20child%20and%20understand%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande%2C%20Images%20Courtesy%20Harpreet%20Grover%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1724424039000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Fharpreet-1724420589.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D362788%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Inspired%20by%20his%20experience%20as%20a%20new%20father%2C%20Harpreet%20Singh%20Grover%2C%20who%20goes%20by%20the%20name%20%E2%80%98The%20Curious%20Parent%E2%80%99%20on%20social%20media%2C%20helps%20parents%20understand%20their%20children.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Sowmya%20Mani%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A12%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F362788%2Fcurious-parent-harpreet-